kflow files and the ClawSweeper app token does not have workflows permission\n\nInherited issue-closing references from the source PR:\nCloses #42213\n\nCo-author credit kept:\n- @siewcapital: Co-authored-by: Siew's Capital Jarvis <264786654+siewcapital@users.noreply.github.com>\n\nfish notes: model gpt-5.5, reasoning high; reviewed against ae868b7b18df.\n",
